{"tid":2284592,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"毒撚戀上網友「仙氣妹」被騙32萬人仔，見真身後立即崩潰！","createTime":"2020-11-13T11:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T17:12:53.000Z","uid":38539,"like":44,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4c16add7fc3f9f8a6b6b723bea38ac9e33548a","tid":2284592,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:50:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtjvZZe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtjvZZe.jpg&h=410cab79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸湖南一名29歲單身劉姓宅男，去年11月在線上遊戲認識一名張姓女網友，看到對方照片就深深被吸引，立即展開猛烈追求，狂匯32萬人民幣（約新台幣137萬）後，終於追到人，最後雙方見面夢幻完全破滅，本尊體重竟然直逼100公斤，讓他崩潰驚喊：「比我還魁梧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qONUHcw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqONUHcw.jpg&h=268ed541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《株洲晚報》報導，劉男與張女在網路遊戲互稱「公婆」，還在微信互加好友，張女在微信發的每張自拍照都是皮膚白皙、身材纖細，打扮時髦，還說自己正打算出國留學，讓劉男相當動心，兩人聊著聊著就談出了感情。<br />\n<br />\n交往之後，張女一直以生病、沒生活費、沒錢繳房租為由，向劉男要錢，劉男為了討她歡欣，總是每求必應，不斷匯錢給張女，可是對方就是不肯見他一面。<br />\n<br />\n今年2月份，張女又說父母出車禍，急需一筆救命錢，劉男二話不說，立刻匯給她20多萬人民幣（折合台幣86萬元），劉男後來經過打聽，找到了張女的住處，可是一見到本尊完全崩潰：「她體重約100公斤，比我還魁梧」。因張女還不出總計32萬元人民幣（約台幣137萬），只好報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n經警方調查，張女沒有固定工作，去年開始上網盜用正妹照騙財，她說：「一開始只是想試試，沒想到劉男深信不疑，還動了真感情」。另外還有2名男子跟她「網戀」，張女詐財金額超過新台幣172萬元。"},{"pid":"f7835aea836fff9bc8efb89212e44501b961da3a","tid":2284592,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:50:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201112001596-260409?chdtv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201112001596-260409%3Fchdtv&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIu6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=3ef91e64\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20201112001596-260409?chdtv</a>"},{"pid":"d1f88c45ce098ded5df6991e1ab402f59e738030","tid":2284592,"uid":66324,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:52:25.000Z","msg":"唔係肥仔咪算好彩, 都仲係女人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f8060475b5ec6772fbb7ce6d59d5bc77ebc8290","tid":2284592,"uid":54337,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ih1.redbubble.net/image.1041941384.3560/flat,750x,075,f-pad,750x1000,f8f8f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fih1.redbubble.net%2Fimage.1041941384.3560%2Fflat%2C750x%2C075%2Cf-pad%2C750x1000%2Cf8f8f8.jpg&h=97f98076&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28d825e39be8e5192f7e1f9ce8fe59cfd634f50d","tid":2284592,"uid":19552,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:53:40.000Z","msg":"豬扒都係肉"},{"pid":"a24a05142942fc384ff1487d514b29c08c287792","tid":2284592,"uid":317498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"肥婆都係肉"},{"pid":"e2ba836f5440d23e24261de5b90aad9b9230b3e6","tid":2284592,"uid":89064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:54:23.000Z","msg":"寧願打飛機"},{"pid":"a1022de83be9f1b192c7554eb2b018b928bf1257","tid":2284592,"uid":263183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:54:34.000Z","msg":"無咩分別"},{"pid":"c19a3d3e54ba7ad9989f0befb4976ef236de96fd","tid":2284592,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"755037e327c2d26d0a36dbc6a743a0f88631132e","tid":2284592,"uid":266654,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:04:27.000Z","msg":"本身張相都唔知邊撚度仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚見到真人，我就真係嚇撚到仙遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f2a6da306be44043e5b293c0f32944cfc93a37","tid":2284592,"uid":59328,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UoayXYq.jpg\" data-thumbn